notes.text:
An update is available for google-api-python-client, python-gflags, python-oauth2client, python-uritemplate.
This update affects Rocky Linux 8.
A Common Vulnerability Scoring System (CVSS) base score, which gives a detailed severity rating, is available for each vulnerability from the CVE list
notes.title: Topic

notes.text:
Rocky Enterprise Software Foundation OpenStack Platform provides the facilities for building, deploying
and monitoring a private or public infrastructure-as-a-service (IaaS) cloud
running on commonly available physical hardware.

For additional information about the items in this advisory, refer to the
Technical Notes chapter of the Release Notes,
https://access.redhat.com/documentation/en-us/red_hat_openstack_platform/16
.2/html/release_notes/chap-technical_notes

This advisory is provided by Ctrl IQ, Inc for Rocky Linux systems. For more information about CIQ security practices, visit https://ciq.com/security.
